16:
Louder, my dear! Fill the air with that
GORGEOUS voice of yours!
25:
...Hell of a way to kick off the new
year.
30:
Levy's training to improve her
self-esteem, in order to fully
embrace her popular status.
43:
Worse, the RATE it's growing at is
ridiculous! It's genuinely scary!
46:
I just finished up a New Year's
photoshoot earlier! The bar of
expectations won't stop going up!
50:
I'm just an adventurer! Not even a
particularly impressive one, either!
55:
...An idol needs to be able to look
themselves in the mirror, but Levy's
struggling to do that alone.
59:
That's why she needs a special
instructor to help bridge the gap
between her lack of self esteem and
her popular public image!
64: Why are you so weirdly into this?
68:
B-but! Don't you think we're going
about this the wrong way?
70:
You're just telling me what to think,
right? Even if I try to force myself to
think like that, I—
79:
There's no need to force yourself. A
beautiful woman stands here before
us, and we are merely striving to
prove that to you!
84:
You're so strong and cool, Levy. And
you look very cute in that outfit, too.
88:
Well, regardless of how we might go
about convincing you... Your
popularity alone is proof enough of
your charm.
93:
...I-I'm honored to hear you all say
that.
95:
However, I feel as though I'm simply
overrated by the fans. I think their
love is wasted on me...
101: Marguerite, you know what to do.
105:
Levy Gracia! Do you dare to curse
the RADIANT aura of light that
surrounds you?
107:
Will you go so far as to curse others
who aspire to be like you? Answer
me!
113:
The essence of both strength and
beauty is an unyielding spirit. The
ability to believe in my own potential!
117:
Marguerite, give me another lesson...
Give me as many lessons as it takes!
121:
Heh-heh, that spirit of yours... Simply
MAGNIFICIENT!
125:
Stand tall, fair Levy! Declare your
beauty to the heavens with all your
might!
132: Let it be known! I, Levy Gracia...
138:
Lady Levy... Um, Levy! Thank you for
seeing me today!
140:
I was over the moon just to get your
signature, but getting to talk to you
one-on-one like this? I, I...
152:
Are you nervous? You're trembling,
and your face is beet red.
156:
Lady... Levy? Is th-that you? You
seem d-different...
160: Levy Gracia, the one and only.
162:
We can hold each other's hands...
See?
165:
There's no need to be afraid. We're
together, with no one to bother us.
167:
Give me everything of you. Here in
my arms, let your heart melt... And
we'll share a memory we'll never
forget.
183:
Who the hell even is this... And what's
"giving a perfect response to the
fans" supposed to mean?
186:
This is just another aspect of that
woman's beauty. Her potential is
simply LIMITLESS!
191:
L-Levy... Can I have a "perfect
response" too?
199:
I don't know how things ended up
the way they did, either!
204:
I was feeling a little funny back then,
that's all! So please, just forget
about it and—
211:
No FAIR! I'm not gonna stop trashing
you at the next talk event!
221:
That's the part where you're
supposed to tell me I'm a bad girl,
push me up against a wall and lift
up my chin!
234:
...Well, huh. We've got to explore new
possibilities whenever we can, right?
